verbose_text: ELISA showed extremely low yield in both active (sham 0.00540 +/- 0.00672 ng/mg; MI 0.0498 +/- 0.0302 ng/mg) and total TGF-beta levels (sham 0.312 +/- 0.096 ng/mg; MI 0.510 +/- 0.066 ng/mg) and failed to demonstrate any significant increase of either active or total TGF-beta levels in the post-MI myocardium compared with the sham myocardium.
